{"tid":1419920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好講咁多先，一定要煲大荃灣恐怖襲擊&同志們，這邊","createTime":"2019-08-06T03:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:55:55.000Z","uid":58335,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0daa308de085b23739bb7a9dc9c8a144a936dc61","tid":1419920,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"今日我見啲新聞只係定性琴晚荃灣恐怖襲擊係打鬥<br />\n但係明明琴晚有人用埋刀斬傷好多人 <br />\n仲嚴重過721<br />\n但好似連登以外冇咩人關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n你哋覺得會唔會有香港人用蝗話仲講同志們，這邊？？<br />\n<br />\n擺明係有疑似老解/國安/武警黎左執法<br />\n咁同出咗老解有咩分別？<br />\n但我見連登以外嘅注視度又係好似好低<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻煩大家一定要煲大佢</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e79952c003e5de4e1fc5c950a799675b861e46","tid":1419920,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8af0a089cf8014e451905cf3b15b38c9f151df0","tid":1419920,"uid":296734,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:05:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3018977b488d37ea44b774d485ac92c8b4b43165","tid":1419920,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"仲有黃大仙熄街燈"},{"pid":"98e7489d9396630e89e29ba634a6d2327dff1250","tid":1419920,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8af0a089cf8014e451905cf3b15b38c9f151df0","tid":1419920,"uid":296734,"like":